{{ if eq (printf "%s" .Format) "html" }}
**Main mockup.html** loads components via `fetch()` + `innerHTML`:

```html
<div id="section-name"></div>
<script>
  function loadComponent(id, file) {
    fetch(file).then(r => r.text()).then(h => document.getElementById(id).innerHTML = h);
  }
  loadComponent('section-name', 'components/SectionName.html');
</script>
```

Component files are HTML **fragments** (no `<html>`/`<body>` wrapper), sharing the main page's styles.
{{ else }}
**Main mockup.jsx** imports and renders all components:

```jsx
import SectionName from './components/SectionName';
export default function Mockup() {
  return <div><SectionName /></div>;
}
```

Component files export default React function components.
